The,Tolq,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,human,translation,into,their,applications,Users,send,Tolq,their,content,and,that,content,is,divided,into,sentences,which,are,sent,to,professional,translators,Users,will,only,be,charged,once,per,unique,sentence,no,matter,how,many,times,a,sentence,is,submitted,After,translation,content,is,put,back,together,and,sent,back,to,the,user